<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="预定义变量" id="预定义变量">预定义变量</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

语法:

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    __LINE__
    __FILE__
    __DATE__
    __TIME__
    __cplusplus
    __STDC__</pre>
<p>
以下预定义变量可能因编译器而异，一般的理解为：

</p>
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <code>__LINE__</code> 和 <code>__FILE__</code> 变量记录了编译器的当前处理行和当前处理文件。</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <code>__DATE__</code> 变量包含当前文件被编译的日期，格式为：月/日/年。</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <code>__TIME__</code> 变量包含当前文件被编译的时间，格式为：时:分:秒。</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <code>__cplusplus</code> 变量只有在C++程序中才被定义；一些老编译器也可以为<code>c_plusplus</code>。</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <code>__STDC__</code> 变量在编译C程序的时候被定义，许多编译器在编译C++代码时也会定义此变量。</div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
<!-- EDIT1 SECTION "预定义变量" [1-738] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit2"><a name="gcc特有变量" id="gcc特有变量">GCC特有变量</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

以下是GCC特有变量。While they are not specifically preprocessor macros they are <a href="http://gcc.gnu.org/onlinedocs/gcc/Function-Names.html" class="urlextern" title="http://gcc.gnu.org/onlinedocs/gcc/Function-Names.html"  rel="nofollow">magic</a> and can be used the same way:

</p>
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <code>__func__</code> contains the bare name of the function</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <code>__FUNCTION__</code> is another name for <code>__func__</code></div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> The <code>__PRETTY_FUNCTION__</code> contains the type signature of the function as well as its bare name. </div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
<!-- EDIT2 SECTION "GCC特有变量" [739-] --></div>
